Mr Vincent Idowu, father to Ex- BBNaija housemate, Tboss is dead. Idowu died on Friday, September 20th. His death was confirmed by Tboss and her brother Christopher, on their Instagram page. Christopher wrote, “To say that I’m devastated is an understatement. Rest in peace Dad! We didn’t always agree but I always understood you.” T-boss also wrote, “So many words left unspoken forever. “We wasted so many time being angry, so many years and for what exactly, nothing.” Recall that the 35-year-old welcomed her daughter this month after she denied that she was pregnant. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.